    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "A *miniaturization module* is a bulky clockwork belt interwoven with clear rubber tubing. These tubes are filled with distilled liquid magic, which serves as a power source. While wearing a *miniaturization module*, you gain a +1 item bonus to checks to Escape.",
    "traits": [
      {
